Products.Description: Meet 4-UP—the ultimate sit-to-stand experience with a dynamic, telescoping gaslift. Unlike traditional solutions that limit users to sitting or perching, 4-UP unlocks the full potential of a sit-to-stand desk, allowing seamless movement between sitting, standing & every position in between. Featuring seat depth adjustment, ergonomic forward tilt & Via Seating’s proprietary injection-molded comfort foam, 4-UP delivers unmatched comfort & support. It’s no surprise it became the first-ever Best of NeoCon Business Impact award winner for an ergonomic desk chair.

Select from white or black frames with matching arms & bases. Also available as task stools.

The All-Ways chair is a versatile, stackable and nesting seating solution designed to meet the needs of dynamic spaces. Its ergonomic design provides optimal comfort and support, making it perfect for various settings from training rooms to break areas. Winner of the Best of NeoCon GOLD award for stacking, All-Ways combines a sleek, modern aesthetic with durable construction for long-lasting use. Experience the ultimate in functionality and style with All-Ways.

Astro redefines seating with a dynamic, interactive experience unlike any other. Effortlessly rock & swivel, finding balance from any angle. Designed to make a statement, Astro offers versatile textile options to complement any space or design concept. Its high-back design provides a sense of privacy, perfectly framing the user within. The nest-like seat delivers exceptional comfort—ideal for quiet reflection or a moment of relaxation.

Brisbane HD is a heavy-duty 24/7 task chair designed for ultimate durability & support. Built with a spacious “D” seat & a 450 lb. weight capacity, it delivers exceptional ergonomic performance for any user. Featuring synchro control technology with optional seat depth adjustment & ergonomic forward tilt, Brisbane HD adapts to individual needs for all-day comfort. Backed by a 12-year warranty, including proprietary comfort foam & labor, it’s a powerhouse solution for demanding work environments.

Experience the refined elegance of Carmel—an executive, conference & “execu-task” seating series designed for both style & performance. With subtle curves & classic tuxedo styling on the front & back, Carmel makes a statement from every angle. Its proprietary comfort foam, injection-molded around an automotive-inspired 100% steel framework, ensures lasting comfort & durability. Ideal for private offices with an ergonomic quick-adjust synchro control & 8-way adjustable arms, as well as conference rooms, jury seating & beyond.

Where contemporary design meets European sophistication, Chico emerges—a versatile lounge series that blends soft angles with bold lines. Chico makes a statement in any space while delivering exceptional comfort. Settle into a thick layer of Via Seating’s proprietary injection-molded comfort foam, expertly crafted over a durable metal framework for lasting support. Customize your look with multiple base options, including a sleek & sturdy wire-frame x-base. Whether in lounges, collaborative spaces or private offices, Chico offers the perfect balance of style, comfort & functionality.

Coleurí is a bold multifunctional seating series by the world-renowned, award-winning designers at Dorigo Design. This striking collection embraces simplicity while showcasing an elegant Italian high-design aesthetic. Available in a range of dipped-look colors, Coleurí adds a dynamic touch to any space. It offers versatile options, including a sleek poly seat, an upholstered seat, or a fully upholstered chair. For added sophistication, choose the wood base option to elevate its timeless appeal.

Comet invites you to relax in style, offering a perfect blend of comfort & sophistication. Settle into its contoured mid-back design & seamlessly integrated arms, crafted for both support & aesthetic appeal. Experience effortless movement with 360° swivel & rock, giving you full control over your motion-lounge experience. Customize your look by mixing upholstery options across the seat & back, creating a design that’s uniquely yours.

Inspired by the 50th anniversary of the moon landing, Italian designer Angelo Pinaffo envisioned the Eclipse series—a seamless fusion of form & function. With its continuous, fluid lines mirroring the elliptical orbits of planets, Eclipse embodies both elegance & lightness. This award-winning collection, recognized with Red Dot Design, ADEX Platinum, HiP Honoree & Best of NeoCon GOLD, delivers vintage-inspired beauty with essential comfort. Explore the original Eclipse or take it outdoors with the sleek Eclipse Wired version.

Redefine lounge seating with Edge—a fusion of bold design & versatile functionality. With a wide range of base options, Edge seamlessly adapts to lounge, executive guest, lobby, conference & breakout spaces. Personalize its look with multiple upholstery choices & elevate the design with contrasting stitching that highlights its sleek curves & signature edges. Experience the perfect balance of innovation & comfort, where striking aesthetics meet luxurious seating in a chair designed to stand out.

The award-winning Genie® evolves with Genie Flex®—a task chair engineered for next-level support & durability. Featuring a robust Thermoplastic Polyurethane (TPU) material, commonly found in high-performance running shoes & heavy-duty industrial seals, Genie Flex® delivers exceptional comfort with its 4-way stretch design. Built to withstand daily wear, it is abrasion & scratch-resistant, grease & oil stain-resistant, and bleach cleanable. Plus, TPU is 100% chlorine-free, PVC-free & fully recyclable, making it a smart, sustainable seating choice.

The award-winning Genie® series is celebrated for its sleek design, advanced ergonomics & exceptional versatility. Its signature genie lamp-shaped back frame, paired with 4-way stretch elastomeric mesh, enhances both aesthetics & upper body mobility. Offering six seat sizes within the same framework, along with a wide selection of adjustable arms & a choice of synchro or body balance technology, Genie® delivers a fully customizable, ergonomic sitting experience tailored to any user.

Jeté embodies graceful motion, slimline elegance & award-winning innovation. This triple award-winning series combines signature comfort with a sophisticated, contemporary profile, available in high & mid-back designs. Its sleek silhouette is further enhanced by exquisite detailing, including shadow tufting, parallel & box hand-sewn patterns. A perfect balance of beauty & function, Jeté is designed by Gensler as product design consultant & Via Seating, redefining modern seating with timeless style & sustainable craftsmanship.

Joí is simplicity with presence. It draws the eye and offers a casual sitting experience wherever it is placed. A tantalizing array of color options are offered across seat trim. This rests atop a polished, beech wood base available in low stool, counter stool & bar stool heights. The sleek, bar stool affords an ample foot ring color matched to the seat trim to create synergy and continuity in design.

Step back in time with Linate—the original signature chair that launched in 1987, the same year Via Seating was born. A true classic, Linate combines timeless design with exceptional structural integrity, making it a standout choice for a variety of spaces, from contemporary offices to more traditional settings. Its refined silhouette & enduring craftsmanship ensure both style & durability, offering a seating solution that remains as relevant today as it was at its inception. Available in high & mid-back options, the mid-back model also offers jury seating configurations, providing added versatility for courtroom & institutional settings. Linate is a testament to Via Seating’s legacy of quality, innovation & design excellence.

Meteor lights up any space with a bold fusion of style & playfulness, making a striking entrance into the lounge scene. A sleek, smaller-scale cousin to Astro, Meteor offers a refined yet dynamic presence. Settle into its inviting form & experience the Via motion-lounge sensation—effortlessly swiveling & rocking for a truly engaging sit. Designed to balance sophistication with a touch of fun, Meteor is the perfect addition to modern lounges, collaborative spaces & beyond.

Imagine the perfect seat for quiet contemplation—one that supports your focus while allowing for undisturbed reflection. Whether admiring a work of art or simply taking a moment to pause, you need a perch that is comfortable yet refined, elegant yet approachable, simple yet timelessly crafted. Terra is a smart blend of affordability & ergonomic excellence, designed to adapt to a wide range of users. Offering five seat sizes—from petite (AA) to large (C)—and a ratchet mid-back, Terra provides personalized support for any body type. For added versatility, stool & tall stool kits can be applied, making Terra a perfect solution for both seated & elevated workstations.
